title: The Villainess Is a Marionette
description:
“Beauty cannot be a real power.”
Cayena Hill, who was praised as the greatest beauty in the Empire, only knew about the life of luxury and flattery.
She was destined to face her villainous end as her tyrant younger brother used her to obtain the throne. Later on, she was killed by her crazy husband after being put through abuse and confinement.
…until one day, I became ‘that’ Princess Cayena.
“I will make you the emperor.”
“…Do you mean me, sister?”
“In return, you shall grant me my freedom.”
A rose with poisonous thorns, a beauty that lures death…
I will take control of my life this time.
